<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
	  <meta charset="utf-8">
	  <title>Condominio</title>
	  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

	  <!-- Le HTML5 shim, for IE6-8 support of HTML elements -->
	  <!--[if lt IE 9]>
	    <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
	  <![endif]-->
	  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
	  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", :media => "all" %>
	</head>
  <body>

    <div class="container-fluid">
      <div class="top">
        <div class="ltop">
          <span><%= link_to "eumoro.no", root_url %></span>
          <span><%= link_to "Sign in Facebook", usuario_omniauth_authorize_path(:facebook) %></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="hero-unit">
          <h1>Heading</h1>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Aenean commodo ligula eget dolor. Aenean massa. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Donec quam felis, ultricies nec, pellentesque eu, pretium quis, sem. Nulla consequat massa quis enim.</p>
          
          <p><%= link_to "Saiba mais", '#', :class => 'btn btn-success btn-large' %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="span6">
          <h3>Condominios j√° utilizando</h3>

          <i class="icon-user"></i>
          <% @condominios.each do |condominio| %>
          <%= link_to condominio.nome, condominio %>
          <% end %>
        </div>

        <div class="span5">
          <%= form_for(:usuario, :as => :usuario, :class => "well form-inline", :url => session_path(:usuario)) do |f| %>
            <%= f.email_field :email, :class => "input-small", :placeholder => "Email" %>
            <%= f.password_field :password, :class => "input-small", :placeholder => "Senha" %>
            <%= f.submit "Sign in", :class => "btn btn-success" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  </body>
</html>